Production use is permitted provided that you do not offer the Licensed Work as a Managed Infrastructure Audit Service.

A “Managed Infrastructure Audit Service” means a commercial offering that allows third parties (other than your employees and individual contractors) to access the functionality of the Licensed Work as a hosted, cloud-based, or remotely operated service, including but not limited to:

- Infrastructure audit-as-a-service
